        {
            "title": "布倫特原油本周累漲14%，站穩100美元上方！特朗普威脅對胡塞武裝採取行動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\" data-component=\"blocks\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"布倫特原油本周累漲14%，站穩100美元上方！特朗普威脅對胡塞武裝採取行動\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/6c6b835aa87d78871cc6b4e82b4cb69492799b977525108ee1d94fdd893654c4/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fcontent-media.investing.com%2Fnews%2FLYNXMPECB60NB_M.jpg\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">布倫特原油本周累漲14%，站穩100美元上方！特朗普威脅對胡塞武裝採取行動</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週五亞洲交易時段，油價保持穩定，布蘭特原油進一步站穩每桶100美元上方。美國與伊朗之間的緊張局勢持續升溫，中東地區供應中斷跡象未見緩解。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·特朗普於週四發出嚴厲警告，揚言將對伊朗及也門胡塞武裝採取重大軍事行動，起因是胡塞武裝對紅海油輪發動攻擊，令這場衝突開闢了新的戰線。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間下午8:14(北京時間次日上午8:14)，布蘭特原油期貨上漲0.2%，報每桶100.85美元；美國WTI原油期貨則上漲0.4%，報每桶92.53美元。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>油價邁向連續第三週大幅上漲</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">布蘭特原油本週觸及兩個月高位，累計漲幅達14%，在美伊軍事衝突重燃的背景下，已連續三週錄得顯著漲幅。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-35ea83a3-e877-380d-bb0b-d90772458069-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價最新一輪上漲，源於受伊朗支持的也門胡塞武裝對紅海沙特油輪發動攻擊，令市場對石油供應中斷的憂慮進一步加深。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">胡塞武裝將攻擊目標鎖定在曼德海峽的過往船隻，而美國與伊朗之間的互相報復式打擊已持續近兩週，霍爾木茲海峽的航運交通也因此大受影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·特朗普於週四揚言，將對伊朗及胡塞武裝在紅海的攻擊行動予以「重大軍事懲罰」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據《紐約時報》報道，伊朗已拒絕美國支持的停火提案，兩國之間的外交斡旋目前幾乎已全面破裂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普於週四稍後表示，「伊朗的資金」將用於賠償「船隻、貨物或任何相關損失」。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>胡塞武裝在紅海攻擊沙特油輪</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週油價漲勢的主要推手，是胡塞武裝在曼德海峽對運載沙特石油的船隻發動攻擊。此前，胡塞武裝已揚言對沙特阿拉伯實施海上封鎖。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">沙特阿拉伯原本借道曼德海峽，以繞開霍爾木茲海峽的運輸干擾，但胡塞武裝在該地區的持續挑釁，預示中東石油供應將面臨更多衝擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全球石油庫存在上月短暫回升後，預計7月將再度趨緊，而中東局勢的持續惡化，令供應改善的前景愈發渺茫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價急漲加劇了市場對能源驅動型通脹持續高企的憂慮，這或將促使全球主要央行進一步收緊貨幣政策立場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong>七月限時開搶！InvestingPro 4折到手，AI選股名單即刻用，跑贏標普500近3倍，全年冇更平，錯過就走寶！</strong><a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>即刻點擊訂閱</em></strong></a><strong>！</strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/3bcb9a3d393dbbd3e1658d406afca8ab1207efa668a46d6bfc045af2e6091dd3/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fcontent-media.investing.com%2Fhk%2Fcontent%2Fd433b5fa3bdecfd5727ef66e0eca0902.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></blockquote></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B8%83%E5%80%AB%E7%89%B9%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E6%9C%AC%E5%91%A8%E7%B4%AF%E6%BC%B214-%E7%AB%99%E7%A9%A9100%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E4%B8%8A%E6%96%B9-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E5%B0%8D%E8%83%A1%E5%A1%9E%E6%AD%A6%E8%A3%9D%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-025348969.html",
